Suns coach Monty Williams was obviously frustrated, giving one statement during his postgame press conference, but not taking any questions.<br />
<br />
&quot;Until we learn how to play the right way consistently, we're just going to have a lot of nights like this,&quot; Williams said. &quot;That's the deal.&quot;

